metadata_description: Invoke-DOSfuscation is a PowerShell v2.0+ compatible cmd.exe command obfuscation framework. (White paper: https://www.fireeye.com/blog/threat-research/2018/03/dosfuscation-exploring-obfuscation-and-detection-techniques.html)
Revoke-Obfuscation is a PowerShell v3.0+ compatible PowerShell obfuscation detection framework. used for de obfuscating powershell scripts
